title: Real Power (Person of Interest)(2 x 5)
author: Person of Interest Highlights
comment: "The politicians come and go, but we'll be here forever"
“Building Steam With a Grain of Salt” is the song
“Who needs money, when you have real POWER!
It's ironic that Lester Freamon became a mob boss.
The head of HR actually used to be a good guy, but got became evil because he didn't get his pepper steak.
description:
